## Fields

- `team_name` — name of the specific team as written, or `null` if none given. Examples: `"Payments Platform"`, `"Oncology Nursing"`, `"Store Operations"`, `"Fleet Operations"`.
- `team_function_tags` — English-normalized free-text tags describing what the team does. Examples: `["backend", "payments", "infrastructure"]`, `["cardiology"]`, `["customer service", "front-of-house"]`, `["audit", "compliance"]`.

